videos.headline: Lawrence drops dime for 35-yard TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence connects with Amari Rodgers in stride for a 35-yard Clemson TD.

videos.headline: Etienne breaks free for long Clemson TD run
videos.description: Travis Etienne slices through the Wofford defense and jets to the house for a 47-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Etienne breaks free for long Clemson TD run) 2019/11/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson's Dixon bounces to outside for TD dash
videos.description: Lyn-J Dixon uses his speed to cut to the outside and motors to the end zone for a 19-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson's Dixon bounces to outside for TD dash) 2019/11/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Etienne bolts to the house for an 86-yard TD
videos.description: Travis Etienne breaks free again for an 86-yard Clemson touchdown, his second score of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Etienne bolts to the house for an 86-yard TD) 2019/11/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence lasers TD to Higgins
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence rips a pass over the middle to Tee Higgins for the 22-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence lasers TD to Higgins) 2019/11/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence strolls into the end zone for a TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence keeps it himself gets into the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown to balloon Clemson's lead to 42-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence strolls into the end zone for a TD) 2019/11/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ross tightropes sideline on TD from Lawrence
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence throws his third touchdown of the game, as Justyn Ross catches the pass and tightropes the sideline for a 34-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ross tightropes sideline on TD from Lawrence) 2019/11/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence, Etienne tag team to pummel Wofford
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence and Travis Etienne have a field day against Wofford, combining for more than 400 yards and five touchdowns in Clemson's 59-14 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Lawrence, Etienne tag team to pummel Wofford) 2019/11/2 ESHEET SOTFULL
